Chamberlain
v.
Newton, et al. 39P14-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016

Robert S. Chamberlain, Pro Se.

Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, For State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th of March 2016 by Petitioner for Complaint/Grievance/Petition:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."
